{"title_page": "Sonia Prim", "text_new": "{{short description|Spanish footballer}}\n{{Infobox football biography\n| name           = Sonia Prim\n| image          =\n| caption        =\n| fullname       = Sonia Prim Fern\u00e1ndez\n| birth_date     = {{Birth date and age|df=yes|1984|11|5}}\n| birth_place    = [[Madrid]], [[Community of Madrid]], [[Spain]]\n| height         = {{convert|1.60|m|ftin|abbr=on}}\n| currentclub    = [[Levante UD (women)|Levante]]\n| clubnumber     = 4\n| position       = [[Defender (association football)|Right back]]\n| youthyears1    = 1997\u20131999\n| youthclubs1    = [[CD Lourdes]]\n| years1         = 1999\u20132004\n| clubs1         = [[CF Pozuelo (women)|Pozuelo]]\n| years2         = 2004\u20132010\n| clubs2         = [[Levante UD (women)|Levante]]\n| caps2          = 132\n| goals2         = 12\n| years3         = 2010\u20132012\n| clubs3         = [[Atl\u00e9tico Madrid (women)|Atl\u00e9tico Madrid]]\n| caps3          =\n| goals3         =\n| years4         = 2012\u2013\n| clubs4         = [[Levante UD (women)|Levante]]\n| caps4          = 156\n| goals4         = 9 <!-- 144-9 before the 2018-19 season -->\n| pcupdate = 13 April 2019\n| nationalyears1 = \n| nationalteam1  = [[Spain women's national football team|Spain U19]]\n| nationalcaps1  = \n| nationalgoals1 =\n}}\n{{spanish name 2|Prim|Fern\u00e1ndez}}\n'''Sonia Prim Fern\u00e1ndez''' (born 5 November 1984) is a Spanish [[Association football|football]] [[Defender (association football)|defender]] who is the [[Captain (association football)|captain]] of [[Primera Divisi\u00f3n (women)|Primera Divisi\u00f3n]] club [[Levante UD (women)|Levante UD]].<ref>[http://www.levanteud.com/noticias/19560/sonia_prim_regresa_al_levante_ud_femenino.html Sonia Prim returns to Levante UD women]{{dead link|date=May 2018 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref> She previously played for [[CF Pozuelo (women)|CF Pozuelo]] and [[Atl\u00e9tico Madrid (women)|Atl\u00e9tico Madrid]].<ref>[http: